@startuml
|System|
start

:Verify User Role;
:Load User Dashboard;
:Open Asset Handling;

:Check Specific Asset;
:Check Asset Availability;

if (Asset Available?) then (yes)
    :Record Reservation Request with Date/Time Range;
    :Update Asset Status to Reserved;
    :Update Status Across Network;
    :Send Reservation Confirmation to User;
    :Log Reservation Timestamp;
else (no)
    :Detect Reservation Conflict;
    :Identify Conflicting User/Reservation;
    :Notify User of Conflict Details;
    :Provide Alternative Asset Suggestions;
endif 

stop
@enduml
